<TEXT>
<P>
Church &amp; Dwight Co., Princeton, N.J., makers of Arm &amp; Hammer brand 
products, has named Spencer J. Volk, 55, to the newly created post of president 
and chief operating officer. Volk, who had been president of Tropicana Products 
Inc., most recently ran the Volk Group, which was formed to acquire Tropicana 
from Kohlberg Kravis Roberts. Seagrams, however, bought Tropicana. Prior to 
Tropicana, Volk was vice president-marketing and sales for refrigerated foods 
at Beatrice. 
</P>
</TEXT>
