July 18, 1989, Tuesday, San Diego County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Part 4; Page 2A; Column 5; Financial Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
30 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
SAN DIEGO PEOPLE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Michael Spencer has been named division manager for Sunland Consolidated new 
division, Sunland Homes of Nevada; Dan Fitzpatrick has been named sales manager 
for Villa Trinidad. 
</P>
