</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
MORNING REPORT: PEOPLE WATCH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By ALEENE MacMINN, Arts and entertainment reports from The Times, national and 
international news services and the nation's press. 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
June Lockhart and Jon Provost will be together again with Lassie on a 
silver-anniversary reunion episode to be shot next week for MCA-TV's new 
syndicated "Lassie" series. Provost was the orphan Timmy on CBS' "Lassie" 
series from 1957-64, and Lockhart was on the same show from 1958-64. The new 
show stars Dee Wallace Stone, Christopher Stone, Will Nipper, Wendy Cox and 
Lassie.ALEENE MacMINN 
</P>
</TEXT>
