<P>
Ferruzzi Releases Letters: Ferruzzi S.p.A., the Italian agricultural giant that 
plans to sue the Chicago Board of Trade after being ordered to liquidate large 
positions in soybean futures, released letters of protest in support of its 
free-market stance from the grain buying agencies of the Soviet Union and 
China. Several independent traders and firms have privately come out in support 
